Interface DistributionProcessor<T extends MutableDistribution>

All Known Implementing Classes:
DoubleArrayLinearScaler, DoubleArrayNormalizer, DoubleArraySquareNormalizer, DoubleArrayZscoreScaler
public interface DistributionProcessor<T extends MutableDistribution>

An operator that performs some transformation on a distribution of the generic type. Such a processor may smooth a distribution, normalize it, etc.
